# Commercial Packages & Modular Architecture

See [COMMERCIAL_PACKAGES.md](../../COMMERCIAL_PACKAGES.md).

## Rules

1. Build as modular SaaS ‚Äî customers pay only for licensed modules.
2. Package resolution maps `subscriptions.plan_key`: starter, growth‚Üíprofessional, business, enterprise.
3. Gate features with `is_tenant_module_enabled()` ‚Äî never expose unlicensed capabilities.
4. Tenant isolation mandatory ‚Äî no cross-tenant module or usage data.
5. Feature flags: enabled, disabled, trial, beta, deprecated, enterprise_only.
6. Routes: `/app/settings/billing`, `/app/settings/modules` (spec `/admin/*`).
7. i18n: `customerApp.commercialPackages.*`, `platform.commercialPackages.*` in en/no/sv/da.
8. Integrates existing `plans`, `subscriptions`, and License Center ‚Äî do not duplicate payment logic.

